	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hi. I just started a Erudite Magician, and i am wondering what i should do... Where i should spend my practices and all that other newbie stuff.<br><br>Thanks for your input<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
