<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=97305801513591></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f97305801513591><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=12&mid=97305801513591>RE: Newbie</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=12&mid=97305801513591#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Nov 1st 12:53 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Since you are Erudite I say first say that you get your Newbie Robe from Erudin Palace.<br>After that put some points into piercing, and maybe 1hb or 2hb (whichever you plan to use).<br>Also a point it Evoc, Abjur, Conj (they'll all max out sooner or later so no need to worry on that).<br>After doin the points thing go to the docks and go to Qeynos.<br>Get a bind there and stay there to kill <br>At lvl 4 go to Qeynos Hills and kill there<br>After that at about lvl 12 go to FP and bind yourself there and head to NRO and kill Dervs in a group.<br>After a little while (maybe lvl 14 or so) you can head to Oasis and kill Orcs.<br>If you pass lvl 17 post another message and I'll tell ya more.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
