	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2><br>My mage is lvl 13 and he kicks ass, all you need to do is max out your int.  I was able to find jewlry to improve my int and other stats fairly eassy so you don't need to worry about that.<br>Also, at lvl 1, even though you won't be meleing very much later on(my 13 mage has to mele maybe %25 of the time) put all five of your pr into piercing, it will give you an advantage over the mobs since the only useful lvl 1 spells are the summons(and true north until I got sense heading up).<br><br>Eumno 13th generation mage on Morris-Thule<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
