	   <tr><td colspan=2>This trick only works for high level magician pets (probably 40 or above). Here's how it goes:<br><br>Give your pet two Gnoll Hide Lariats. The mob will spends a very large portion of the battle stunned and unable to do anything. This works because your pet attacks so many times that at least one of the lariats procs frequently.<br><br>This works best if you use whatever pet has the highest dexterity (I think Air Elementals).<br><br>The only drawback is the annoyance of finding people willing to sell Gnoll Hide Lariats, or getting some yourself.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
