	   <tr><td colspan=2>"I am a 45 mage, Yellow cons are though, even with a pet that has about 3000 hp."<br><br>This is called BS. At level 45 no pet, not even the earth pet, has anywhere 3k hp. The level 49 earth pet is the only pet with 3k hp. This strategy is also not very good becuase if you don't outdamage your pet they get half of the exp. from the kill. It is better to take low blues that can be killed quickly giving very low downtime. This is also called the pet recasting trick which has already been written by someone on this forum.<br><br>At 45 spectors and the shadowknight/shaman in rathe mountains are good choices. A level 45 magician can also take seafuries at this level, but they aren't as good of exp. as the spectors or duel troll spawns in Rathe Mountains.<br><br>If you like grouping I suggest lower guk or solusek B(nagafen's lair). Kedge Keep is also a great place, especially if you are going to fight the 'boss' of the zone(forget name). He drops the level 49 Elemental Staff of Mastry: Water. Of all these Guk is my favorite.<br><br>I hear that there are also a TON of great spots in Kunark, however I don't have Kunark (video card not good enough).<br><br>Happy Hunting.<br><br>Zuranthium/Divineshadow/Corpusnuntia/Sunsong/Naltec/Natalos/Plantmaster<br><br>Player of many characters on the Nameless.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
