	   <tr><td colspan=2>I never used Fire effectively (except when greenie farming) until now, at 29.  I never used air effectively until 20.  At 16 my effective pets were water and earth.  I don't know if this was just lack of experience or not.  My Magician was my first character (and ONLY character until he hit level 20, except a Troll Shaman I played to level 3 or 4 before deleting).<br><br>Soloing Outdoors: Probably earth.  That level 16 Shock is devestating, and you are most effective having your pet pin down the target so you can unload the flames on it.<br><br>Soloing Indoors: Same, plus Earth prevents runners.<br><br>Grouping Indoors/Outdoors: While post 20 any of the non Earth pets has been great in a group (and Earth too if we lacked a Snarer/Darknesser) at 16 I used water.  He tanks great, and does fantastic damage, and doesn't break Snares.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
