	   <tr><td colspan=2>There are a couple of magical armors for casters that I know of. Neither is particularly expensive, but they aren't easily obtained and you hardly ever see them auctioned. One is Netted Armor that drops off various froglocks in Innothule Swamp and related areas. The second is Gossimer, which drops off Festering Hags in Unrest. Of the two, gossimer seems to be a bit better (higher AC vs. weight), and is a very attractive white color- very scarce. My gnome magician wears a gossimer robe, and is constantly asked if it is some sort of new Robe from Kunark (I wish...). there may well be others, but I am regretfully ignorant of what/where they might be.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
