	   <tr><td colspan=2>Im sorry but the sutff we can summon is NOT useless.  At least one of my group members almost always runs out of food or drink while were hunting/questing.  Also bandages - people who are wounded will almost always pay a few pp for a stack of them (especially if you bind their wound int he case of newbies with low skill level).  Plus, summoned things help you make friends, people dont mind being handed something even if it will disappear when they log out.  And I really dont like to go buy weapons for my pets just to lose them and the money that they cost - its much better to summon them.  Oh and when your a real newbie - those staff spells help - especially when you first start fighting wisps since the staffs are magic - people always ask me to summon them magic weapons when they're just starting to fight wisps or for corpse retrieval when they dont have a weapon on them.  And although i dont yet have some of the 50+ spells - im really looking forward to some of those conjuration ones. :)  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
