	   <tr><td colspan=2>Trust me, with out a good tank up in front your pet will die before they do at 35.  What I did was group with my level 40 paladin friend and killed HGs in Rathe mountains.  Had him buff me and my pet and he tanked while my pet did additional damage (Water works good here.  You really can't stun giants so no use for air)<br><br>If the paladin got low on HP, he would just root the giant and Gheal him self to full while my pet did a little tanking.<br><br>But with a little well placed nuking the giant never lasts that long =)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
